 832:Generated_Source\PSoC4/PWM.c **** *  applicable for Timer/Counter with Capture or in Quadrature Decoder modes.
 833:Generated_Source\PSoC4/PWM.c **** *
 834:Generated_Source\PSoC4/PWM.c **** * Parameters:
